{"tid":785373,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"受性醜聞所累 奇雲史帕西新戲美國開畫得989蚊票房","createTime":"2018-08-19T07:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T09:55:37.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d570369fd9591635fb247f407b15c7cc9961ec27","tid":785373,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:15:25.000Z","msg":"金像影帝奇雲史帕西（Kevin Spacey）隨住#MeToo風暴被爆出性醜聞非禮男生，事業立即急轉直下，主演電影、劇集都被飛起，而最近佢拍落嘅電影《華爾街狼群》（Billionaire Boys Club）剛於美國上畫，但票房慘淡只得126蚊美金（約港幣989元）。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街狼群》由兩位上位年輕男星泰隆艾格頓（Taron Egerton）及安索艾果特（Ansel Elgort）主演，奇雲史帕西都有份，但因為被性醜聞影響，全個美國得10間戲院上，連紐約同洛杉磯都無戲院上，難怪票房慘淡，今次亦係奇雲史帕西演藝生涯中收得最差嘅作品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180819/58582024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F58582024&d=nQmoHIdi91iVTh58cZr5n7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=78c7c10b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F58582024&h=2a40e098\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180819/58582024</a>"},{"pid":"4c900a9c5418f8ae7a4adf23fb9d2a1dc3f54066","tid":785373,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:28:45.000Z","msg":"為咗兩條仔入去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b12f9c6e4158086da6c6aa7814909429e8779a","tid":785373,"uid":60588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:55:37.000Z","msg":"套野重要叫Billionaire <span style=\"color: red;\">Boys</span> Club<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}